premise_source_doc_sentence: The movie stars Kimberly Williams-Paisley , Tammy Blanchard , and Matt Letscher and is based on the book Amish Grace : How Forgiveness Transcended Tragedy , Jossey-Bass , 2007 , , by Donald Kraybill , Steven Nolt , and David L. Weaver-Zercher .
